00:03:54.860 --> 00:03:57.500
We have 1,000
staff inside Syria.

00:03:57.500 --> 00:03:59.870
They are the people
who are being bombed

00:03:59.870 --> 00:04:02.600
by conventional weapons
and now by chemical weapons

00:04:02.600 --> 00:04:05.270
in eastern Damascus.

00:04:05.270 --> 00:04:08.630
