00:04:46.730 --> 00:04:50.300
the fundamental issues of
whether or not victims of war

00:04:50.300 --> 00:04:55.070
have rights is now at issue,
at stake, at risk in a way

00:04:55.070 --> 00:04:56.460
that it hasn't
been for 70 years.

00:04:56.460 --> 00:04:59.240
And so it's really a
mixture of, if you like,

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:04.010
