00:39:36.360 --> 00:39:39.480
But we're excited about this
economic opportunity model.

00:39:39.480 --> 00:39:40.749
We want to spread it.

00:39:40.749 --> 00:39:43.290
We're trying to tap in some of
the financial institutions who

00:39:43.290 --> 00:39:45.885
work on the community
reinvestment trust areas.

00:39:45.885 --> 00:39:48.810
It's not quite the
right wording of it.

00:39:48.810 --> 00:39:50.160
So I think it's a good model.

00:39:50.160 --> 00:39:53.280
We have quite a lot of
experience of small business

00:39:53.280 --> 00:39:55.860
loans for women entrepreneurs
around the world

00:39:55.860 --> 00:39:59.400
which are also very, very
successful and really quite

00:39:59.400 --> 00:40:00.910
positive.

00:40:00.910 --> 00:40:03.510
There's a big debate,
