00:40:05.820 --> 00:40:07.770
on the sorts of the
problems of poverty,

00:40:07.770 --> 00:40:10.200
because there's
quite a lot of data

00:40:10.200 --> 00:40:14.110
now to show that it's not
as simple as it sounds.

00:40:14.110 --> 00:40:16.770
And there's now quite
a lot of dispute

00:40:16.770 --> 00:40:18.990
about the long-term
income effects,

00:40:18.990 --> 00:40:20.740
but that's for another day.

00:40:20.740 --> 00:40:22.740
JACQUELLINE FULLER:
Unconditional cash transfers

00:40:22.740 --> 00:40:25.080
