become 10,000--

00:43:58.690 --> 00:44:01.180
Googlers who are
supporting IRC, you'll

00:44:01.180 --> 00:44:05.390
get to see more of the
difference that you're making.

00:44:05.390 --> 00:44:10.790
But I think generally we've got
an amazing social media team,

00:44:10.790 --> 00:44:12.880
but they're doing
it on a shoestring.

00:44:12.880 --> 00:44:15.460
The most powerful
thing is to get

00:44:15.460 --> 00:44:18.040
people talking in
their own voices

00:44:18.040 --> 00:44:20.620
with their own stories
and their own credibility,

00:44:20.620 --> 00:44:22.990
because it's so much
harder to point the finger

00:44:22.990 --> 00:44:24.760
and say, no, that's spin.

00:44:24.760 --> 00:44:26.920
It can't be spin if you
are the person who's

00:44:26.920 --> 00:44:27.961
actually been through it.

